import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'

    return (
        <Dropdown>

        <Dropdown.Menu>
            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">All Emitters</Dropdown.Item>

            <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Geologic Sequestration of CO2 (RR)</Dropdown.Item>

        </Dropdown>
    )

}

export default ButtonTypeA
